   * and the protection is received in the event of default between attachment and detachment points.
   * A value of 'Sell' implies selling protection.
   */
  @PropertyDefinition(validate = "notNull")
  private final BuySell buySell;
  /**
   * The underlying resolved CDS index that this tranche is based on.
   * <p>
   * This reference CDS index provides information about the constituent legal entities.
   */
  @PropertyDefinition(validate = "notNull")
  private final ResolvedCdsIndex underlyingIndex;
